The paper deals with motion planning for legged locomotion, which is a topic related to robotics (cs.RO). The use of polytopes and constraints on accelerations also suggests a systems and control (cs.SY) aspect to the research. Additionally, the paper mentions the potential use of the AWP and FWP in robot design, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), or computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories.
